 \"And in 2020 he released his debut albumA Human's Journey.\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5043, \"end\": 5050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2895456222439742e-18, \"text\": \"Journey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dodge_Journey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is also a keen artist and has a room at his home where he draws and paints, and is also a fan of manga and anime.\", \"from\": 5053, \"to\": 5169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At 8 years old, Noah was drawing Spider-Man in a cityscape,\\\" his father Kevin Lyles toldThe Undefeated.\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5188, \"end\": 5192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.7607305327911992, \"rank\": 0.31452478971228787, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Spatial visualization, he's always been great with that.\\\"\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having won his first world title over 200m in 2019, Lyles returned from Tokyo 2020 disappointed to take home only a bronze over the distance.\", \"from\": 5335, \"to\": 5476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5387, \"end\": 5392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.939063916418533, \"rank\": 0.06489024039665443, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 5407, \"end\": 5412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7583383635385677, \"rank\": 0.3186725716091627, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In preparation for Paris, he put more time into the indoor scene and the 60m distance at which teammate Coleman excels, pushing him close in Glasgow earlier this year to take his first indoor medal.\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5497, \"end\": 5502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3180637803674876e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5582, \"end\": 5589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Coleman\", \"score\": 0.9599450562256033, \"rank\": 0.04172628173232758, \"text\": \"Coleman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Coleman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Coleman\"}, {\"begin\": 5619, \"end\": 5626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9989869814306543, \"rank\": 0.001014045813097835, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles subsequently showed himself to be a true team player by making a surprise appearance in the United States 4x400m quartet for the final at the World Indoors, picking up a second silver of the Championships.\", \"from\": 5678, \"to\": 5889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5776, \"end\": 5789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999197986406765, \"rank\": 8.003892026763728e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_bas